Dylan Sprouse https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dylan_Sprouse 0 Dylan Thomas Sprouse (born August 4, 1992) is an American actor and the twin brother of Cole Sprouse. He is known for his role as Zack Martin on the Disney Channel series The Suite Life of Zack Cody and its spin-off, The Suite Life on Deck.
